{
  "stem": "18102.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 22.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if they didn't, they would have been caught in the trap, because it wasn't long after that that the Germans captured Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And all of the Jewish community, which was a thriving-- hundreds of thousands of Jews were exterminated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There were only 10,000 Lithuanian Jews left in all of Lithuania, never mind Vilna, after the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so that visa saved the lives of many thousands of Jews, among them the Melamdoviches.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not sure whether you had to identify-- I, I suppose that was a fictitious place that you had to say.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was only a transit visa, that's right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it, it, it identified, for most people, that they were on their way to Curacao.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you didn't have to be on your way to Curacao.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could be on your way to anywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The visa was transit, and the idea was to get into Japan, from which you would leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody really wanted to stay in Japan, anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was foreign territory of a real different nature that most of the refugees didn't want to remain in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father applied along with, as I said, thousands of others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Fortunately, we got the visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, of course, there was this huge danger, that by applying for permission to leave with the visa, he had to identify himself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he had to identify himself as Isaac Moishe Melamdovich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If it was connected by whoever was the Russian administrator in, in, in, in granting permission to leave that we were really the Melamdoviches that were wanted in Bialystok, then, of course, the fate would have been Siberia, at least.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
